title: Wednesday Post Show (10-20-21)
itunes:title: Wednesday Post Show (10-20-21)
description:
Bobby talks about Garth Brooks announcing he will be playing 2 shows at the Ryman in Nashville. Bobby shares a story about a time he went to test out new material at the Bluebird and has a very awkward moment. Eddie had to return the Hyundai Tucson back to Bobby and it was sad. We also get into a discussion of how Bobby was worried of dying alone. Mike D shares a situation in which construction workers are using the bathroom in his backyard. We also play another round of Blank Slate.
